<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>سَيَأْتي الْيَوْمُ المَوْعُودْ * وَسَتَلْتَقِي الجنُودْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>بِالدَّمِ سَوْفَ نَجُودْ * وَسَتَسُودُ الأُسُودْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
